《'''新觀察家'''》（{{lang-fr|'''''Le Nouvel Observateur'''''}}，{{IPA-fr|lə.nu.vɛ.lɔb.sɛʁ.va'tœʁ}}；常簡寫作：'''''L'OBS'''''），是一家[[法語|法語]][[新聞雜誌|新聞類周刊雜誌]]，總部位於[[巴黎|巴黎]]。

自1964年創立伊始，該報便涉足政治、經濟等領域。其新聞覆蓋範圍包括[[歐洲|歐洲]]、[[中東|中東]]和[[非洲|非洲]]的政治、商業及文化問題。被描述為“法國吃魚子醬的左派人士的半官方機構”（quasi-official organ of France's gauche caviar）。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://select.nytimes.com/iht/2006/06/20/world/IHT-20politicus.html|title = Chirac's Potential Heirs Keeping Change Hidden|publisher = International Herald Tribune, republished by [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date = June 20, 2006|accessdate = 2008-09-12|last = Vinocur|first = John|archive-date = 2012-10-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020021535/http://select.nytimes.com/iht/2006/06/20/world/IHT-20politicus.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

